  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<h3 id=\"id-1.18.13-Announcements\">Announcements</h3><ul><li><p>The Mobile Defenders integration has been retired.</p></li></ul><h3 id=\"id-1.18.13-NewFeaturesforAdvancedandProfessionalUsers\">New Features for Advanced and Professional Users</h3><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933443149/Required+Fields+for+Repair+Devices\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933443149\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Device Required Fields</a> - Customize the required fields for device intake on Repair Tickets.</p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1937801227/Third-Party+Marketing+Consent\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1937801227\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Third-Party Marketing Consent</a> - Prompt staff to ask customers for their consent to allow approved third parties to contact them.</p></li></ul><h3 id=\"id-1.18.13-Improvements\">Improvements</h3><ul><li><p>Customize overtime dashboard alerts based on hours defined in Location Settings.</p></li><li><p>Improvements to Square payment performance involving connection issues and duplicate payments.</p></li><li><p>Improvement to the date selection UI when using filters.</p></li></ul><h3 id=\"id-1.18.13-BugFixes\">Bug Fixes</h3><ul><li><p>Fixed an issue that caused an error if the ticket item preview was hidden in Quick Sale Optimization settings.</p></li><li><p>Fixed the duplicate &quot;Receive SMS Messages&quot; field when updating Validation Rules.</p></li><li><p>Fixed an issue that affected backorder items on Internal Purchase Orders.</p></li><li><p>Fixed an issue that affected the location count total when making subscription changes through Account Settings.</p></li><li><p>Fixed the blank balance issue when sending an Automated Notification with the Ticket Action trigger.</p></li><li><p>Fixed an issue that caused no results to return when filtering Invoices for &quot;All Locations&quot;.</p></li><li><p>Fixed the &quot;Inactive&quot; attribute when filtering the Catalog.</p></li><li><p>Fixed missing details (price, subtotal, and signature) line on Qpop screens.</p></li></ul>",
